	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes, Dex will affect your success rate now.&nbsp;&nbsp;Verant will be implementing it (if they havent already)<br><br>Basically<br><br>Int = How often you succeed<br>Wis = If you gain skill points or not<br>Dex = How often you succeed<br><br>What does this mean to you?  Probably nothing.  As a human wizard, I have 230int, 120dex, 120wis.  I can boost my dex into the 150s with items, without dropping int below 200.<br><br>With that configuration, I have already completed 6 silk swatchs (the swatches you get from combining the silk threads) with only a 50 skill in tailoring.  Success rate is about 60% for me.  I hope to complete the shawl soon<br>&nbsp;<br>Raquelis Crimsonfire<br>54th Channeler<br>Torvonnilous Server</td></tr>
